_:Nffcde37563c0455b8443bb55bb3e181e <http://schema.org/description> "High Speed Two (HS2) Limited is the company responsible for developing and promoting the UK’s new high speed rail network. It is funded by grant-in-aid from the government. HS2 Ltd is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Transport ." .
